All scripts in this directory assume the following:
- all files are stored in the current working directory
- the default mailman configuration file is mailman.yml
- the cookies are read/stored in mailman.cookies

Supported command-line options:
--config <YAML config file>
--cookie <cookie file>


The mailman.yml file has the following stucture:

---
example:
  uri: http://lists.example.com/mailman/listinfo/example
  email: user@example.com
  password: s3kr3t
  admin_password: b1gs3kr3t
  moderator_password: s3kr3t
